    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391100/extras/08c11a4dd8e8c7baebab13fc77be7b31.poster.avif?t=1682821176\" width=616 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391100/extras/08c11a4dd8e8c7baebab13fc77be7b31.webm?t=1682821176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391100/extras/08c11a4dd8e8c7baebab13fc77be7b31.mp4?t=1682821176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391100/extras/8b5c473683d53df923027cf94e0a952e.poster.avif?t=1682821176\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391100/extras/8b5c473683d53df923027cf94e0a952e.webm?t=1682821176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391100/extras/8b5c473683d53df923027cf94e0a952e.mp4?t=1682821176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Button VR Expeditions is an immersive and challenging virtual reality game that takes players on a thrilling adventure through a series of dangerous and exotic environments. Using cutting-edge VR technology, players can fully immerse themselves in the game world and interact with objects and obstacles in a natural and intuitive way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391100/extras/e5708dfa0d2b0955a47d757a4b05b3ce.poster.avif?t=1682821176\" width=616 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391100/extras/e5708dfa0d2b0955a47d757a4b05b3ce.webm?t=1682821176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391100/extras/e5708dfa0d2b0955a47d757a4b05b3ce.mp4?t=1682821176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391100/extras/d5c9c2c2e173e914c8de5722291e3828.poster.avif?t=1682821176\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391100/extras/d5c9c2c2e173e914c8de5722291e3828.webm?t=1682821176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391100/extras/d5c9c2c2e173e914c8de5722291e3828.mp4?t=1682821176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>One of the key features of Button VR Expeditions is the game's dynamic and unpredictable challenges. In addition to the increasing difficulty curve, players must also contend with a variety of hazards and obstacles that can appear at any moment. A time-based danger worm adds an extra layer of tension and strategy to the gameplay, forcing players to move quickly and stay alert to avoid being caught. Meanwhile, a physics-based elevator adds a new dimension to the puzzles, requiring players to carefully balance weight and momentum to reach their goals. And if that wasn't enough, a deadly laser threatens to zap players out of existence, adding an element of risk to every move they make.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391100/extras/23a1de2ae2cb718dc52c008d0bc26b91.poster.avif?t=1682821176\" width=616 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391100/extras/23a1de2ae2cb718dc52c008d0bc26b91.webm?t=1682821176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391100/extras/23a1de2ae2cb718dc52c008d0bc26b91.mp4?t=1682821176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But despite the dangers, there's a rich world to explore in Button VR Expeditions. From dense jungles to treacherous caverns, each environment is filled with secrets and challenges that will test players' skills and wits. Whether navigating through narrow passages, solving complex puzzles, or battling against dangerous creatures, every moment in Button VR Expeditions is a thrilling adventure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391100/extras/7dc25d1905b4fc2657c72fe4532ac7e9.poster.avif?t=1682821176\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391100/extras/7dc25d1905b4fc2657c72fe4532ac7e9.webm?t=1682821176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391100/extras/7dc25d1905b4fc2657c72fe4532ac7e9.mp4?t=1682821176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Overall, Button VR Expeditions is a must-play game for anyone looking for a thrilling and immersive VR experience. With its dynamic challenges, rich environments, and cutting-edge VR technology, the game offers a truly unforgettable adventure that will keep players coming back for more.",
